HEADWORD: Matchmaker
<hw>Match"mak`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
who makes matches for burning or kinding.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who tries to bring about marriages.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Matchmaking</ent>⟦br⟧
